data.title: Dino Georgakis - Football
data.meta_description: Dino Georgakis (55) LB  - 2012: Saw action in four games as a freshman … Collected his first career solo tackle against Saint Anselm (10/20) …
data.text:
2012: Saw action in four games as a freshman … Collected his first career solo tackle against Saint Anselm (10/20) … Tallied a solo tackle against Saint Anselm (11/10).

Before Merrimack: Attended Milton High School ... Also ran track and field ... All-state linebacker junior and senior year ... Also named team captain and team MVP junior and senior years.

Personal/High School: Born Septempber 15, 1992 ... Son of Tony and Victoria Georgakis ... One sibling Sophia ... Computer Science major at Merrimack.

CAREER HIGHS

Tackles: 1, Saint Anselm, 10/20/12 (1-0); Saint Anselm, Nov 10, 2012 (1-0)
